Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:05.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿It's hard to prosper while so far apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.40,0:00:07.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Exactly who is Hondou Eisuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.05,0:00:08.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿A case on the Teimuzu River!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.28,0:00:09.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Something new is beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.68,0:00:11.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Recognizing that single truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.13,0:00:12.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿A child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.54,0:00:14.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿His name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:03.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Did it return yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:05.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Mizunashi Rena's conciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.78,0:02:07.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:10.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's suffered from blunt force trauma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:14.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿The doctor first said one month.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:18.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿He also said if it took two, it could take longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:21.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Assuming her condition worsened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:24.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.96,0:02:30.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿The longer she takes, the higher the\N﻿chance we'll make a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.76,0:02:38.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Then we really should move her to a\N﻿different hospital, preferably in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:39.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:44.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿That's exactly what they're expecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:46.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:51.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Well, if that's the case, let's catch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:54.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Don't you think she's perfect bait?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:57.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿B-Bait?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:02:58.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:02.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Do we know anything about Mizunashi Rena's past?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:06.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Actually, everything she said on and to Nichiuri TV was fabricated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:12.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿That includes her birthplace and her hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:17.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿I guess that means we don't even know about her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:23.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Then, a strange name like "Mizunashi\N﻿Rena" must be a joke as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:25.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿A joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:27.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Mizunashi is 0,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:34.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fncentury gothic\fs40\bord2\shad0\b1\3c&H7C1006&}"Mizu" is water, "nashi" is without: "without water" which equals 0.\N {\alpha&HFF&\t(1960,1961,\alpha&H00&)}Rena can be pronounced Reina. "Rei" is 0, "na(na)" is 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:30.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Rena is 07.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:34.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,007.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:35.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:46.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Shadow of the Black Organization:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:47.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿The Young Witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:51.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Ah, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:55.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Even if I did say that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:59.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿it was only because you asked me to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:00.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿You should talk to your husband about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:07.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.73,0:04:10.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,YOU INSENSITIVE BASTARD!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:16.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Who was that on the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:22.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Some woman who asked me to follow her cheating husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:28.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿"It's because of you that he left me and that I'm miserable!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:30.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿That's what she said, but she isn't exactly loyal either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:34.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Geez, I'd like to be James Bond right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.84,0:04:38.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:41.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:48.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿He only wears expensive brand name clothes,\N ﻿drives super cars, has all that high tech stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:51.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿He can follow someone easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.29,0:05:12.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿And me, I've got normal clothes, a beat up rental car...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:16.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿And a partially working camcorder for following spouses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:33.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Not to mention, he gets all the hot chicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:36.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿I get a middle aged woman yelling at me over the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿What went wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:45.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿This coffee's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.91,0:05:46.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Is this a brand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:53.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Nope, it's not It's a new filtered coffee that\N﻿was on sample sale at the supermarket.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:58.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿The ad had something about collecting\N﻿points to win a really cute coffee pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.09,0:06:03.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Well, just instant from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:05.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿You...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.35,0:06:10.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're gonna complain, you won't be drinking any!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.69,0:06:10.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:15.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Hot, hot, hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:17.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-﻿You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:20.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Hondou Eisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:22.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿H-Hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:26.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh, I'm so sorry! Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:27.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:31.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿I think I stood up on the wrong leg as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:34.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿So, how'd you get in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:37.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿We met at the supermarket by chance so I brought him along.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:42.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Detective Mouri, you said I could come over whenever I wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:44.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:47.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm here to help! I'll answer the phone, or anything, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:54.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Yes, this is the Mouri Detective Agency!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:57.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Hello? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:00.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:06.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿That's odd, they hung up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:11.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿You hung it up yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:18.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿You're best at not touching anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:20.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿I didn't sense him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:25.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'll get you a towel, Eisuke-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.62,0:07:26.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:25.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿When he came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:28.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Maybe I just wasn't paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:30.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:33.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿I got it, Eisuke-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:34.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:37.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh, I'm sorry, I didn't see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:38.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:42.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Or maybe his shadow's just too bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:53.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Detectives sure have a lot of free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:55.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:58.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Might be different if somebody hadn't hung up on a client.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh, this manga's taking a break next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:06.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Man, I want to know what happens next.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:09.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿The break's for the author to collect information.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:12.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿But this could require investigation as well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:14.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:20.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿See, the only reason they ever give is that the\N﻿author is collecting information, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:24.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿He could have just quit because he didn't like the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:28.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿He could have caught the flu and is now unable to continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:32.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Or maybe he was kidnapped and is being held somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:35.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿I don't think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:41.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿But, it's like that actor who disappeared half a\N﻿year ago when they said he was taking a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.67,0:08:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿But he was actually sick, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:47.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿There was someone recently, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:49.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:51.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Right, they were on TV a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:55.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿They were there one minute and gone the next!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.98,0:09:01.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh, right! You mean Itakagi Roku?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:07.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿You know, the musician who had his\N﻿breakthrough and debut last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:09.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Are you sure you haven't heard of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:11.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Y-Yeah, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:16.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿I thought so, but Sonoko told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.58,0:09:19.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿He's only been performing for one year,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:22.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿But he already needs a break? Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:23.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:26.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Is Sonoko-neechan a fan of his?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:29.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Yeah, because he plays indie music.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:35.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿The girls only go after him because he has money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:38.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿He's almost 007.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:40.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿That guy is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:45.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿I saw him get dumped over a bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:49.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:54.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Ever since he saw an ad for Itakagi Roku's latest CD on TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:57.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Takumi-kun has been telling you that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:58.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:02.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿He's always saying "Papa, the saw guy is dead."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:04.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿The saw guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.90,0:10:13.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fncentury gothic\fs40\bord2\shad0\b1\3c&H7C1006&\fade(500,100)}Album Cover "Silver Sky, Volume 1"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:07.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿It's because he looks like a saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:12.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿It's probably because of his silver haircut.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:17.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿But since there weren't any news reports on TV or on the radio,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:20.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At first I did not believe my son...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:23.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿But when I heard he had taken a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:28.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿I wasn't sure, so I told him we'd visit you, Detective Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:35.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿We tried to call earlier, but someone\N﻿answered and hung up immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:37.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Uh oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:40.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:44.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Hey, Takumi-kun, do you know where this bridge is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:48.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿It seems like such a long time ago.\N﻿I can't remember exactly where, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:51.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿I did hear fireworks there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.30,0:10:55.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Then it could have been New Year's fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:11:01.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Hashiratani-san, do you remember where Takumi-kun was then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.85,0:11:07.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿No, but it must be on the way to the\N﻿temple we visited on New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:13.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿We were in a traffic jam at the time, So I actually got pretty tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:17.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿I guess I was too tired then to notice the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:20.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Can you tell me exactly what happened there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:23.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:28.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿There was a man standing over the\N﻿bridge with a big bag beside him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:33.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿He then just picked up the bag and threw it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.09,0:11:37.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Then, Itakagi-san was in that bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:39.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿But, how do you know he was in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:43.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Before he dropped it, I saw him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:45.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿There was a lot of blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:48.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿But I also saw that guy's head!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.20,0:11:59.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿I really seen it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:10.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be foolish, if someone were walking\N ﻿around with that, someone would notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:14.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿But, it was dark and hard to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:22.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what? If it was actually that dark,\N ﻿how did a little boy like you see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:28.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿It just happened. His head just popped out of the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:32.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿What did the man do after dropping the bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:35.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿He took out stuff from his clothes and dropped them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.32,0:12:43.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿I couldn't see because his body was blocking the way,\N﻿but he was feeling around his clothes for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:45.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Feeling around his clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:49.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Did this guy have something in his mouth before that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:52.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Yeah, there was something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿I see, a cigarette!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:56.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿He had a cigarette in his mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.05,0:12:59.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿That means he was searching for his lighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:02.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿And? Did he find his lighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.89,0:13:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Yeah, but he discarded it after lighting his cigarette.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:08.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿And then, did he stick around?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:12.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Nope, he got in a car and left right after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:16.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Would you be able to recognize his car or face?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:21.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿The car was in the dark, and all I could see was his hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:26.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿But the person did have a strange picture on his arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:29.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Huh? A strange picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:32.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿It was a strange nail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:35.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿A strange nail?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:38.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:41.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿I could see one more thing from the car's window.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:45.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿There was this really big, glowing hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:48.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿A big glowing hammer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.77,0:13:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿A saw,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:53.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a nail,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:54.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿and a hammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:13:59.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Do you think we believe this crap, you little punk!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:01.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿M... Mouri-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.74,0:14:07.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Ah, no... You were just joking with us, right, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:21.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Takumi-kun, it's true, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:21.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:25.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿You aren't...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.64,0:14:28.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Really lying, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:31.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿It's not a lie! I'm really not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:55.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿My chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:15:01.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿If I remove the transmitter and listening device now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:04.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Alright I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:11.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-Boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:53.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Don't tell me, you... followed me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:58.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Of course not...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.73,0:16:01.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:06.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:11.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:15.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿You saved me, by getting my shoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:26.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Really, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:48.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Takumi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:52.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿What this boy has said isn't a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.41,0:16:56.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Huh? What're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:59.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿It's been four days since New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:05.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿If this were true, there would be something\N﻿on the news about a discovered body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:08.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿This is the evening news.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:13.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The male body found floating in\N the Teimuzu river has been identified.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:18.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}His family has confirmed that the body belongs to Itagaki Roku-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:18.63,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Itagaki Roku (22)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:25.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿The body was found stuffed into a bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:30.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Because of the existence of wounds to\N his head likely caused by a blunt weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:35.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿the police are treating this as a murder investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.58,0:17:39.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿It's... It's really true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:47.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Then, Itagaki-san was really placed into a bag, as my son said...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:49.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿It really happened, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:51.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Of course! I don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:55.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Well, that means we should hurry and tell the police, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:18:00.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿That's right. This kid's an eye witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:05.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿But if you go in talking about Itakagi Roku's saw head,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:09.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿About the nail on the criminal's arm,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:12.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿And at the very least...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:19.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿If you tell them you saw a giant glowing hammer from your car,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.79,0:18:23.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿I doubt the police will trust what you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:29.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Besides, you can't remember which\N﻿bridge the body was thrown from.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:31.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Then, let's take Takumi-kun in a car...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:35.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿And retrace everything they did that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.93,0:18:38.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿We already know it was the Teimuzu river.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:44.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿That's true, and I believe you said\N﻿it was on your way to a temple?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.69,0:18:48.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Hashiratani-san, do you remember at least\N﻿some of the route you took that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:50.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:58.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿But, Eisuke-kun, it was great how you knew\N﻿he wasn't lying by touching his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:19:01.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh, no, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:05.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿I was just doing what my father did when I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:08.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿I just got lucky this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.72,0:19:15.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:18.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Which way'd you go at this intersection?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:21.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿The right'll take us to the Big Haido Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:24.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Straight ahead takes us to Haido Central Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:27.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿The left takes us to the New Haido Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:33.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Y-Yeah, going straight is the fastest way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:36.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Then, let's take Haido Central Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:38.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:45.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿They always have sobriety checkpoints that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:48.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿And since I was avoiding them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.13,0:19:51.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Big Haido Bridge then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:55.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Ah, no. There are too many traffic lights that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.26,0:19:58.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿But the other's the longest way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:02.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿You think you can decide soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:04.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.31,0:20:07.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿I always take this road to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.81,0:20:11.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿What bridge I choose depends on my mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:15.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Unfortunately, I don't remember my mood that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:19.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:22.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿You said you remembered the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.58,0:20:24.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:28.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Dad! It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.25,0:20:32.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿We can check each bridge one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:38.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿If you're at this intersection, only those\N﻿three bridges cover the Teimuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:41.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿That's it, right, Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:46.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.98,0:20:49.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:52.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿What's wrong? Don't you feel well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:54.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.61,0:20:56.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.49,0:21:00.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh? I see then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:12.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿I was just doing what my father did when I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.71,0:21:15.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿I just got lucky this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.76,0:21:21.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿No, it wasn't any sort of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.30,0:21:23.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿This wasn't by chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:27.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿He did just what that woman did to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.64,0:21:35.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Sudden irregularities in someone's breathing, their pulse, or\N﻿a widening in their pupils, can tell you if someone's lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:40.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Furthermore, their demeanors and behaviors...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.95,0:21:42.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿They're almost identical.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:46.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought, this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:49.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.26,0:22:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Hondou... Eisuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.22,0:22:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿You...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.19,0:22:14.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿And her...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.11,0:22:17.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Are they somehow connected!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.98,0:22:21.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Mizunashi Rena...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.15,0:22:24.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Known as "Kir" to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:26.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿To the Black Organization!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.51,0:24:04.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, one of the buttons with which the\N poster is attached to the wall is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.39,0:24:06.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.60,0:24:08.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿That's the design I saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.21,0:24:10.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.78,0:24:14.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you already done such a tattoo to anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.32,0:24:19.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.47,0:24:23.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Clearly, this is what he had in mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.62,0:24:25.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Next Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.99,0:24:27.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Shadow of the Black Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.45,0:24:28.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿The Strange Illumination!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.00,0:24:32.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,﻿Next Conan's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.21,0:24:34.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nail & Snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.94,0:24:39.90,Signs,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.75,0:24:37.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Is it really how it seems?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.37,0:24:38.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's how it is!
